item.title: Phoques (Explicative)
item.description: Singular Phoque Type Explicative Meaning To care about (something) Example Sentence “I don’t give two phoques about the actual meaning.” Etymology Derived from the typo a Greek God made in his twitter post about adopting a Phokcs.

item.title: Phokcs
item.description: Plural Phoques, Phoqs Type Noun See also: Phoques (Explicative) Meaning A smol, generally meek, shifty looking mammal.
